    "## 18. Compare 15-minute vs 1-hour accuracy\n",
    "\n",
    "This table checks whether persistence becomes less dominant at the 1-hour horizon.\n",
    "\n",
    "A mature interpretation is not simply “which model wins”, but:\n",
    "\n",
    "> How does model behaviour change when the forecast horizon becomes longer?"
   ]
