    "## 21. Define 1-hour ramp / risk events\n",
    "\n",
    "For the risk version of the project, we define:\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "ramp_1h = PV(t+1h) - PV(t)\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "A large negative ramp means the PV system drops sharply within the next hour. These are the events that can create imbalance exposure.\n",
    "\n",
    "Here we define risk events as the **bottom 5%** of 1-hour ramps in the test set."
